`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Poofin
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax: `` 

 * poofin  <message>

 The standard messages when arriving by goto is 'arrives in a swirling mist'. 
You can replace this message with a message of your own choosing using the
poofin commands.  This messages must include your name somewhere in the string.


 Poofin only shows to characters who can see you.  To change the message seen
when departing, use Poofout.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
